{
  "env": {
    "CLAUDE_CODE_SUBAGENT_MODEL": "sonnet"
  },
  "autoMemoryEnabled": false,
  "hooks": {
    "PreToolUse": [
      {
        "matcher": "mcp__minsky__session_pr_merge",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR/.claude/hooks/block-subagent-merge-without-grant.ts",
            "timeout": 10,
            "statusMessage": "Checking subagent merge-capability grant..."
          },
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR/.claude/hooks/require-review-before-merge.ts",
            "timeout": 15,
            "statusMessage": "Checking for PR review..."
          },
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR/.claude/hooks/require-execution-evidence-before-merge.ts",
            "timeout": 60,
            "statusMessage": "Checking for execution evidence on new test files..."
          },
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR/.claude/hooks/require-deploy-verification-before-merge.ts",
            "timeout": 60,
            "statusMessage": "Checking for deploy-verification commitment on deploy/infra PRs..."
          },
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR/.claude/hooks/block-out-of-band-merge.ts",
            "timeout": 15,
            "statusMessage": "Checking for coupled out-of-band steps in PR body..."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "matcher": "Agent",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR/.claude/hooks/check-prompt-watermark.ts",
            "timeout": 5,
            "statusMessage": "Checking prompt provenance..."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "matcher": "Bash|mcp__minsky__session_exec",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR/.claude/hooks/block-subagent-bypass-merge.ts",
            "timeout": 5,
            "statusMessage": "Checking for subagent bypass-merge..."
          },
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR/.claude/hooks/require-checks-on-bypass-merge.ts",
            "timeout": 30,
            "statusMessage": "Checking required CI status before bypass-merge..."
          },
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR/.claude/hooks/block-git-gh-cli.ts",
            "timeout": 5,
            "statusMessage": "Checking for git/gh CLI..."
          },
          {
            "_comment": "ADR-028 D1 guard-dispatcher pilot (mt#2650): the SOLE settings.json entry for every guard migrated onto .minsky/hooks/dispatch-pretooluse.ts's in-process registry (currently: check-guessed-session-path). Takes the migrated guard's ORIGINAL slot in this block to preserve first-deny-wins execution order relative to its siblings — do not add new individual hook commands here; register them in .minsky/hooks/registry.ts's GUARD_REGISTRY instead.",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR/.claude/hooks/dispatch-pretooluse.ts",
            "timeout": 15,
            "statusMessage": "Running guard dispatcher (PreToolUse)..."
          },
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR/.claude/hooks/block-out-of-band-merge.ts",
            "timeout": 15,
            "statusMessage": "Checking for coupled out-of-band steps in PR body..."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "matcher": "mcp__github__create_pull_request|mcp__github__update_pull_request|mcp__github__merge_pull_request|mcp__github__pull_request_review_write",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR/.claude/hooks/block-github-mcp-pr-writes.ts",
            "timeout": 5,
            "statusMessage": "Checking GitHub MCP PR-write ban..."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "matcher": "Edit|Write|NotebookEdit",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR/.claude/hooks/require-session-for-main-workspace-edits.ts",
            "timeout": 5,
            "statusMessage": "Checking main-workspace edit guard..."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_comment": "mt#2029 R1 consolidation: single PreToolUse block for policy-coverage-detector covering both Claude Code native write tools and MCP session write tools. Consolidating eliminates the double-invocation hazard the prior two-block layout had (if a future matcher refactor accidentally overlapped, both blocks would fire and skew calibration). require-session-for-main-workspace-edits stays in its own native-only block above (session tools are by definition session-scoped, so its guard doesn't apply there).",
        "matcher": "Edit|Write|NotebookEdit|mcp__minsky__session_edit_file|mcp__minsky__session_search_replace|mcp__minsky__session_write_file",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR/.claude/hooks/policy-coverage-detector.ts",
            "timeout": 15,
            "statusMessage": "Checking policy coverage..."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "matcher": "mcp__minsky__session_start|mcp__minsky__tasks_dispatch",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR/.claude/hooks/parallel-work-guard.ts",
            "timeout": 30,
            "statusMessage": "Checking for parallel work..."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "matcher": "mcp__minsky__tasks_create",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR/.claude/hooks/parallel-work-guard.ts",
            "timeout": 30,
            "statusMessage": "Checking for duplicate sibling task..."
          },
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR/.claude/hooks/validate-task-spec.ts",
            "timeout": 5,
            "statusMessage": "Validating task spec structure..."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "matcher": "Skill",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR/.claude/hooks/loop-preflight-pr-merge-check.ts",
            "timeout": 15,
            "statusMessage": "Checking loop preflight (PR/task terminal state)..."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "matcher": "mcp__minsky__tasks_status_set",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR/.claude/hooks/tasks-status-set-guard.ts",
            "timeout": 10,
            "statusMessage": "Validating task status transition..."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "matcher": "mcp__minsky__tasks_status_set|mcp__minsky__session_start|mcp__minsky__tasks_dispatch",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR/.claude/hooks/check-task-spec-read.ts",
            "timeout": 10,
            "statusMessage": "Checking the task spec was read before advancing/binding..."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "matcher": "mcp__minsky__session_commit|mcp__minsky__session_pr_create|mcp__minsky__session_pr_edit",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR/.claude/hooks/check-branch-fresh.ts",
            "timeout": 15,
            "statusMessage": "Checking branch freshness..."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "matcher": "mcp__minsky__session_search_replace|mcp__minsky__session_edit_file|mcp__minsky__session_write_file|Edit|Write",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR/.claude/hooks/check-generated-file-edit.ts",
            "timeout": 10,
            "statusMessage": "Checking for generated file edit..."
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "SessionStart": [
      {
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR/.claude/hooks/session-start.ts"
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "Stop": [
      {
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR/.claude/hooks/typecheck-on-stop.ts",
            "timeout": 60,
            "statusMessage": "Final type check..."
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "SubagentStop": [
      {
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR/.claude/hooks/typecheck-on-stop.ts",
            "timeout": 60,
            "statusMessage": "Subagent type check..."
          },
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR/.claude/hooks/record-subagent-invocation.ts",
            "timeout": 30,
            "statusMessage": "Recording subagent invocation..."
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "SessionEnd": [
      {
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR/.claude/hooks/transcript-ingest-on-session-end.ts",
            "timeout": 45,
            "statusMessage": "Ingesting finished session transcript..."
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "PostToolUse": [
      {
        "matcher": "Write|Edit|mcp__minsky__session_write_file|mcp__minsky__session_edit_file|mcp__minsky__session_search_replace",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR/.claude/hooks/typecheck-on-edit.ts",
            "timeout": 30,
            "statusMessage": "Type checking..."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "matcher": "mcp__minsky__session_pr_merge|mcp__github__merge_pull_request",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR/.claude/hooks/post-merge-pull.ts",
            "timeout": 20,
            "statusMessage": "Pulling latest main..."
          },
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR/.claude/hooks/post-merge-unasked-direction-scan.ts",
            "timeout": 60,
            "statusMessage": "Scanning for unasked directions..."
          },
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR/.claude/hooks/deploy-verification-after-merge.ts",
            "timeout": 30,
            "statusMessage": "Checking for deploy-surface changes needing post-merge verification..."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "matcher": "mcp__minsky__session_start",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR/.claude/hooks/post-session-start.ts",
            "timeout": 10,
            "statusMessage": "Labeling session..."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "matcher": "mcp__minsky__session_pr_create",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR/.claude/hooks/drive-pr-to-convergence.ts",
            "timeout": 5,
            "statusMessage": "Reminding agent to drive PR to convergence..."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "matcher": "mcp__minsky__session_pr_merge|mcp__minsky__tasks_status_set",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR/.claude/hooks/bridge-memory-retirement.ts",
            "timeout": 10,
            "statusMessage": "Checking for bridge memories to retire..."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "matcher": "Bash|Edit|Write|Read|Grep|Glob|mcp__.*",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR/.claude/hooks/two-strikes-record.ts",
            "timeout": 5,
            "statusMessage": "Recording 2-strikes streak..."
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "UserPromptSubmit": [
      {
        "hooks": [
          {
            "_comment": "ADR-028 D1 guard-dispatcher Phase 2a+2b (mt#2652, mt#2687): the SOLE settings.json entry for EVERY UserPromptSubmit guard, all migrated onto .minsky/hooks/dispatch-userpromptsubmit.ts's in-process registry (Phase 2a: substrate-bypass-detector, retrospective-trigger-scanner, pre-narration-detector, causal-premise-detector, code-mechanism-assertion-detector, ask-routing-deferral-detector; Phase 2b: auto-session-title, inject-current-time, inject-git-state, inject-prod-state, inject-dispatch-watchdog, memory-search, skill-staleness-detector, mcp-daemon-staleness-detector, calibration-review-cadence-detector). Do not add new individual hook commands here; register them in .minsky/hooks/registry.ts's GUARD_REGISTRY instead. Timeout=115 (host-cap budget model, hook-files.mdc \"Dispatcher host-cap budget model\"): this ONE process now runs all fifteen UserPromptSubmit guards SEQUENTIALLY, so the host cap must cover the family's worst-case SUM, not one guard's budget. Built from the Phase 2a entry's already-calibrated 60s (covering the six Phase 2a guards' worst-case 65s summed budget, minus a small process-spawn-overhead saving) plus the nine Phase 2b guards' individual worst-case budgets summed (5+5+5+5+5+10+5+5+10=55s): 60+55=115s.",
            "type": "command",
            "command": "$CLAUDE_PROJECT_DIR/.claude/hooks/dispatch-userpromptsubmit.ts",
            "timeout": 115,
            "statusMessage": "Running guard dispatcher (UserPromptSubmit)..."
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}
